room_title: Escape room "The Heist" by Element of Escape in Sarasota
room_address: 1007 Manatee Ave E Ste. A Bradenton, FL 34208
room_description: The Venetia Diamond is one of the rarest and most valuable gems in the world. It is going up on display in your city’s museum. Through a source, you have heard that the museum curator has plans of his own for the diamond. You and your team of thieves can’t bear to stand someone else cashing in on a diamond as precious as this. Can you and your covert team of thieves escape with the Venetia Diamond before the curator can put his own plan into action?
